課程概述 Course Description
       This course, Independent Study in Nursing, is designed to be a student-centered learning process. It provides an opportunity for the student(s) to gain an in-depth knowledge and to critically appraise the existing literature in a specific area of her research interest in Nursing. The syllabus is to be personalized to the student's research interests, and thus is modifiable to create a best learning experience for the student. Specific learning goals are to be listed in the student's Independent Study Plan which is mutually agreed upon by the student and the faculty in charge prior to or at the beginning of the semester.  

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    This course, Independent Study , is designed to be a student-centered learning process. It provides an opportunity for the student(s) to gain an in-depth knowledge and to critically appraise the existing literature in a specific area of her research interest.
     

